1.0.name: wordpress/proliphiq-badge
1.0.description:
Proliphiq.com is a search engine that delivers the most credible social media experts for any topic. The badge allows you to display your credibility and let users rate you (which in turns helps your credibility).

Requires WordPress 3.0 and PHP 5.
